Package menu.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloseCommand
    The CloseCommand class implements the Command interface to close the currently open document.
    EditCommand
    The EditCommand class implements the Command interface to change the content of a specified cell.
    ExitCommand
    The ExitCommand class implements the Command interface to exit the program.
    HelpCommand
    The HelpCommand class implements the Command interface to display information about the commands supported by the program.
    OpenCommand
    The OpenCommand class implements the Command interface to load the contents of a given file.
    PrintCommand
    The PrintCommand class implements the Command interface to print the contents of the table to the console.
    SaveAsCommand
    The SaveAsCommand class implements the Command interface to save the changes made to the table to a specified file.
    SaveCommand
    The SaveCommand class implements the Command interface to save the changes made to the table back to the same file from which the data was read.
